desc_short	-----								Hyper-charged, 5-on-5 tank shooter from the future! Dash, dodge, and crush your enemies with top-notch pilots in fully customizable tanks. Pick your parts and charge into battle in neon-drenched futuristic cityscapes of mayhem.							
